snippet.textDisplay: Gayle expressed on MULTIPLE occasions how Kobe and Gianna's death emotionally 'took her heart and ripped it out' and how it deeply impacted so many people from so many walks of life. People are upset at this interview and probably haven't even watched it in it's entirety. They isolated clips from the interview to make it seem like it was a smear campaign. Gayle King is clearly a warm and empathetic person who was trying to give Lisa Leslie---Kobe's friend, an opportunity to defend his name against the rape accusations that have been brought up by other journalists after his death. This is such a travesty that all of this negative energy is being poured on her name and reputation. Just like all of this negative energy is being poured on Kobe's name and reputation when he was not convicted. We need to be putting energy on uplifting the Bryant family in what is going to be unimaginable sadness and loss.
